description: Enforce English in code and tests, allow Chinese in docs
alwaysApply: true
---

# Language Policy

- Write all code, unit tests, and code comments in English.
- Do not add Chinese text in source/config files (for example `*.ts`, `*.tsx`, `*.js`, `*.vue`, `*.json`, `*.yml`).
- Documentation files may use Chinese (for example `*.md` under `ai-docs/`).
- Keep user-facing data values unchanged when explicitly requested (for example a fixed test input label).
